@startuml
title Architecture Globale (Main Stack)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Client APM" as Client

rectangle "Main Stack" {
  [Nginx] as Nginx
  [Django API] as API
  database "TimescaleDB" as DB
  [Grafana] as Grafana
}

rectangle "Observability" {
  [Prometheus] as Prom
  [Node Exporter] as NodeExp
}

Client --> Nginx : HTTPS
Nginx --> API : HTTP 8000
API --> DB : SQL (PostgreSQL/TimescaleDB)
Grafana --> DB : SQL
Prom --> NodeExp : scrape
Grafana --> Prom : metrics
@enduml
